Master Decision Frame for Future Iteration
Before any major addition, ask: 1. Which section does this belong to? 2. What constitutional parent authorizes it? 3. What dependency does it introduce? 4. What proof target does it move? 5. What drift risk does it create? 6. What section becomes more complex if this lands? 7. Is this core architecture, enabling infrastructure, or product proof?
If those answers are not clear, the addition is not ready.
