Final Position
Hydra should now be built as a federation of aligned sections, not as one continuously mutating mass. The constitutional core remains upstream. The kernel, DLC, and APP tracks should carry the next implementation cycle. VCKB, Garage, and product surfaces should stay aligned to those tracks, but should not be allowed to sprawl the build surface faster than the core can stabilize.
The project is large enough now that alignment is part of the architecture.
